Darkvision						KEY:Darkvision ~ Gnome		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.GnomeRacialTrait.GnomeRacialVision.GnomeSenses		PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Darkvision ~ Gnome],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.GnomeRacialVision,TYPE.GnomeSenses]																									DESC:Some gnome strains have lived in the underground depths for so long they have given up on light entirely and gained darkvision with a range of 60 feet.																																																																							VISION:.CLEAR.Low Light|Darkvision(60)	COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.32
#Eternal Hope					KEY:Eternal Hope ~ Gnome	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.GnomeRacialTrait.GnomeDefensiveTraining.GnomeHatred	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Eternal Hope ~ Gnome],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.GnomeDefensiveTraining,TYPE.GnomeHatred]																							DESC:Gnomes rarely lose hope and are always confident that even hopeless situations will work out. Gnomes with this racial trait receive a +2 racial bonus on saving throws against fear and despair effects. Once per day, after rolling a 1 on a d20, the gnome may reroll and use the second result. This racial trait replaces the defensive training and hatred racial traits.																																																																																																																															COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.15	ASPECT:SaveBonus|+2 racial bonus vs. fear and despair effects
Explorer						KEY:Explorer ~ Gnome		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.GnomeRacialTrait.GnomeHatred.GnomeObsessive			PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Explorer ~ Gnome],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.GnomeHatred,TYPE.GnomeObsessive]																									DESC:Many gnomes are obsessed with seeing as much of the world as possible, rather than perfecting some specific talent or vocation. These gnomes gain a +2 racial bonus on Climb checks and checks for one Knowledge skill of their choice.																														MULT:YES	CHOOSE:SKILL|Knowledge%	SELECT:1														BONUS:SKILL|Climb,%LIST|2|TYPE=Racial								COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.32
Fell Magic						KEY:Fell Magic ~ Gnome		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.GnomeRacialTrait.GnomeMagic					PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Fell Magic ~ Gnome],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.GnomeMagic]								SPELLS:Innate|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=TL|Bleed,10+WIS|Chill Touch,11+WIS|Detect Poison|Touch of Fatigue,10+WIS|PRESTAT:1,WIS=11	DESC:Gnomes add +1 to the DC of any saving throws against necromancy spells that they cast. Gnomes with Wisdom scores of 11 or higher also gain the following spell-like abilities: 1/day:bleed, chill touch, detect poison, and touch of fatigue.																																													BONUS:DC|SCHOOL.Necromancy|1															COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.32
#Gift of Tongues					KEY:Gift of Tongues ~ Gnome	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.GnomeRacialTrait.GnomeDefensiveTraining.GnomeHatred	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Gift of Tongues ~ Gnome],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.GnomeDefensiveTraining,TYPE.GnomeHatred]																							DESC:Gnomes love languages and learning about those they meet. Gnomes with this racial trait gain a +1 bonus on Bluff and Diplomacy checks, and they learn one additional language every time they put a rank in the Linguistics skill. This racial trait replaces the defensive training and hatred racial traits.																																																																																																														BONUS:SKILL|Bluff,Diplomacy|1					BONUS:VAR|AdditionalLanguage|skillinfo("TOTALRANK","Linguistics")								COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.15
Knack With Poison					KEY:Knack With Poison ~ Gnome	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.GnomeRacialTrait.GnomeIllusionResistance.GnomeObsessive	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Knack With Poison ~ Gnome],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.GnomeObsessive,TYPE.GnomeIllusionResistance]																						DESC:Some gnomes have an instinctive understanding of poisons and their uses. Gnomes gain a +2 racial bonus on Fortitude saves against poison and a +2 bonus on Craft (alchemy) checks to make poison. The bonus on Fortitude saving throws against poisons increases to +4 if the gnome accidentally poisons himself when applying or readying the substance. This racial trait replaces illusion resistance and obsessive.																						BONUS:SKILL|Craft (Alchemy)|2|Type=Racial								COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.32	ASPECT:SaveBonus|+2 vs. poison
#Magical Linguist					KEY:Magical Linguist ~ Gnome	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.GnomeRacialTrait.GnomeMagic.GnomeIllusionResistance	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Magical Linguist ~ Gnome],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.GnomeMagic,TYPE.GnomeIllusionResistance]		SPELLS:Innate|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=TL|Arcane Mark|Comprehend Languages|Message|Read Magic|PRESTAT:1,CHA=11				DESC:Gnomes study languages in both their mundane and supernatural manifestations. Gnomes with this racial trait add +1 to the DC of spells they cast with the language-dependent descriptor or those that create glyphs, symbols, or other magical writings. They gain a +2 racial bonus on saving throws against such spells. Gnomes with a Charisma of 11 or higher also gain the following spell-like abilities: 1/day - arcane mark, comprehend languages, message, read magic. The caster level for these effects is equal to the gnome's level.																																																																																																			COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.15
#Master Tinker					KEY:Master Tinker ~ Gnome	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.GnomeRacialTrait.GnomeDefensiveTraining.GnomeHatred	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Master Tinker ~ Gnome],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.GnomeDefensiveTraining,TYPE.GnomeHatred]																							DESC:Gnomes experiment with all manner of mechanical devices. Gnomes with this racial trait gain a +1 bonus on Disable Device and Knowledge (engineering) checks. They are treated as proficient with any weapon they have personally crafted.																																																																																																																										BONUS:SKILL|Disable Device,Knowledge (Engineering)|1																			COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.15
