Wary			KEY:Wary ~ Half-Elf		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.HalfElfRacialTrait.HalfElfAdaptability.HalfElfRacialVision	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Drow Blooded ~ Half-Elf],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.HalfElfRacialVision,HalfElfAdaptability]												DESC:Many half-elves have spent their long lives moving from place to place, often driven out by the hostility of others. Such experiences have made them wary of others' motivations. Half-elves with this trait gain a +1 racial bonus on Sense Motive and Bluff checks.																		BONUS:SKILL|Sense Motive,Bluff|1|TYPE=Racial								COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.42
#Water Child		KEY:Water Child ~ Half-Elf		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.HalfElfRacialTrait.HalfElfAdaptability.HalfElfMultitalented																PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Water Child ~ Half-Elf],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.HalfElfAdaptability,TYPE.HalfElfMultitalented]																			DESC:Some half-elves are born of elves adapted to life on or near the water. These half-elves gain a +4 racial bonus on Swim checks, can always take 10 while swimming, and may choose Aquan as a bonus language.																											TEMPLATE:Aquan Bonus Language																					BONUS:SKILL|Swim|4|TYPE=Racial																								COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.17

