#Warslinger		KEY:Warslinger ~ Halfling		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RacialTraits.SpecialQuality.HalflingRacialTrait.HalflingSureFooted					PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Warslinger ~ Halfling],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.HalflingSureFooted]																DESC:Halflings are experts at the use of the sling. Halflings with this racial trait can reload a sling as a free action. Reloading a sling still requires two hands and provokes attacks of opportunity.																																																																																												COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.21


